WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.760 align:middle line:90%


00:00:06.760 --> 00:00:09.960 align:middle line:84%
>>Fanciful tales have long been
told of a magic spring which

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:12.140 align:middle line:84%
