the search continues,

00:00:23.290 --> 00:00:26.700 align:middle line:84%
but the quest has been taken
up by scientists exploring

00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:30.190 align:middle line:84%
immortality upon a new
frontier-- within the nucleus

00:00:30.190 --> 00:00:31.570 align:middle line:90%
